\begin{document}
}{}\begin{equation*} vpDiff_i \, = \, vpDiff \, \cdot \, \, vInheritance ^{(i - 2)} \end{equation*}\end{document}where vpDiff is the penetrance mean and i is the generation (2 or above). The default value of vInheritance is 0.5 that represent the situation where cases, in each generation, are mated with controls.
